description: This dataset is created by the City's Office of Performance and Accountability using data on household income from the U.S. Census Bureau's Public Use Microdata Samples. It includes data for the following cities: Tampa, Florida; Memphis, Tennessee; Louisville, Kentucky; Nashville, Tennessee; Raleigh, North Carolina; Atlanta, Georgia; Baton Rouge, Louisiana; New Orleans, Louisiana. This data is compiled annually beginning in 2005.
